Creating the selections
The next step is adding the selected values. In most cases, you want this to be the last saved
selections. You can retrieve these values because they are saved for each filter every time a save
action occurs on the container. The PodLoader class provides a getPodFilterById(...)
which returns the selected values for each Pod filter.
Retrieving the saved selections and adding them to the Pod filter:
031      Node genreSelectionNode =
032        getPodFilterById(PODTYPE.MYFAVMOVIES, "genre", document);
033
034      // Convert the Node to an ArrayList.
035      ArrayList<String> selectedGenres =
036       PodFilter.convertSelectionsNodeToArrayList(genreSelectionNode);
